ll bits are made of high-speed, durable stainless steel that won’t rust. Stainless steel is a great material for drill bits because it’s heat and abrasion resistant, ensuring your bits stand the test of time.</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">CUTS HOLES ACCURATELY – Our drill bits are stable and won’t easily break. They are designed to cut holes quickly, accurately and safely in metal and other materials. The twist drill bits spiral with ease and conveniently remove debris from the hole so you can accomplish your project in a timely manner!</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">MULTI-PURPOSE TOOLS – The high-speed drill bits can be used on a number of materials including cast iron, high-temperature alloy plastics, hard plastics, stainless steel, titanium alloy, woods and other soft materials. These are must-have hobby tool essentials for metal-smithing, metalworking and drilling!</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">VARIETY OF SIZES – Our set comes with a variety of drill sizes, ranging from 1.05mm to 2mm. They all feature a universal round drill shank of 3/32”  and will fit drills with a 1/16” shaft. Sizes included: 1.05mm, 1.1mm, 1.15mm, 1.2mm, 1.25mm, 1.3mm, 1.4mm, 1.45mm, 1.5mm, 1.6mm, 1.7mm, 1.8mm, 1.9mm, 2mm</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">COMPACT AND PORTABLE – The twist drill set comes with a black PVC pouch bag that will keep the drills organized when not in use. The pouch is easily foldable so you can store them in your tool box, workshop or travel bag.</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  </table>\n\t\t\t  </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t  </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t  <